grains using spatula then set aside to cool (approx. 45 minutes). Meanwhile, discard cooking liquid and rinse mixing bowl with cold water."},{"content":"Place reserved cooked chicken in mixing bowl and shred <b>4 sec\/\/speed 4<b>. Transfer to a bowl and allow to cool."},{"content":"Add cooled chicken and reserved sauce to large serving dish with couscous and combine using spatula."},{"content":"Place serving dish on mixing bowl lid and weigh in spinach, orange segments and remaining salt and pepper. Remove then stir well with spatula. Serve immediately with pine nuts scattered on top or store in fridge for up to 2 days (see tip)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If large pieces of chicken remain after shredding once, simply shred again <strong>4 sec\/\/speed 4<\/strong>.","If storing in fridge until needed, omit adding pine nuts until just before serving.","The chicken would be great served in a sandwich or with a jacket potato."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 30m","4 portions"]}